'''Nenasha''' was a [[Sullustan/Legends|Sullustan]] [[Pilot/Legends|pilot]] who was once hired by a [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggler]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Sullust/Legends|Sullust]] to work on their [[YT-1300 light freighter/Legends|YT-1300]] [[Freighter/Legends|freighter]]. Nenasha was paid 100 [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] per day for the work.

